    "Gallatin wrote the catalogs, which were issued between 1928 and 1940.": [],
    "In 1926 he co-published with the classicist/collector <a href=\"/hoppinj\">Joseph Clark Hoppin</a> the first fascicule of the prestigious <em>Corpus Vasorum Antiquorum</em> for a United States collection.": [
